  "text": "Our teams\n\n \n \n \n Home\n \n\n Our Team\n\n \n \n \n Team Spotlight:\n\n The Dream Team Behind Our Success\n\n Meet the talented individuals who make our company thrive. Our team is a dynamic blend of creativity, expertise, and dedication. From our innovative managers and detail-oriented analysts to our visionary designers and tech wizards, each member brings unique skills and a collaborative spirit. Together, they drive our mission forward, tackling challenges with enthusiasm and delivering exceptional results. Their commitment and passion are the backbone of our success, making our team not just a group of colleagues, but a family working towards a common goal. \n\n More Services \n \n \n MANAGING DIRECTOR/BUSINESS CONSULTANT\n\n Moses Fongang Kem\n\n \n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n \n \n DEPOT MANAGER\n\n Therese Tayimfor\n\n \n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n \n \n HOD HUMAN RESOURCE AND ADMINISTRATION\n\n Constance Njumanuh A.\n\n \n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n \n \n HOD BUSINESS DEVELOPMENT\n\n Herman Ache Ayiseh\n\n \n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n \n \n ACCOUNTANT\n\n Amadine Mbaku\n\n \n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n \n \n STOCK MANAGEMENT SUPERVISOR\n\n Dominic Nchindia\n\n \n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n \n \n SALES SUPERVISOR\n\n Emmanuel Fongang Teke\n\n \n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n \n \n TERRITORY DEVELOPMENT ASSISTANT\n\n Leonard Tarh Formubad\n\n \n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n \n \n ADMINISTRATOR (Fleet/Procurement)\n\n Jerry Gha Mua\n\n \n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n \n \n CHIEF OF SECURITY\n\n Jonas Fongang N.\n\n \n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n \n \n I.T. OFFICER\n\n Franklin Teba\n\n \n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n \n \n MARKETING MANAGER\n\n \n\n \n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n \n \n SELF COLLECTION MASTER\n\n \n\n \n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n \n Idenau Team \n (The Winners)\n \n Security Team\n \n Stock Operators\n \n Sales Team\n \n Sales Team 1 \n (The Masters )\n The Masters\n\n \n \n Sales Team 2 \n (The Angels)\n The Angels\n\n \n \n Sales Team 3 \n (The Generals)\n The Generals\n\n \n \n Sales Team 4 \n (The Warriors)\n The Warriors\n\n \n \n Sales Team 5 \n (